wer rack and tent it with aluminum foil to protect it.) Remove the cake from the oven, and tip it onto the serving plate.\nServe with hot coffee or tea. The cake is very moist, fragrant and potent.\nWrap securely (or place under a cake cover) and store at room temperature for several days. \nFreeze for longer storage, up to 1 month."
